Advanced encoding/transcoding 104 may be associated with reporting 124. A mobile media platform 100 may facilitate an association of advanced encoding/transcoding 104 with reporting. A combination of advanced encoding/transcoding 104 with reporting may facilitate content discovery 144, ingestion 118, encoding, hosting 132, delivery 120, mediation/settlement 112, and user acceptance of mobile content 128 facilitated by the mobile media platform 100. Reporting may include information about utilization of an encoding/transcoding 104 facility to provide content 128. Encoding/transcoding 104 utilization may be determined based on characteristics of the content 128 delivered, such as live linear streamed content 128 may have utilized on-demand encoding.
