In an embodiment, a pause and resume 114 functionality of a mobile media platform 100 may be associated with advertising content. Content 128 may be advertisements, marketing materials and the like. The content 128 may be an interstitial advertisement, banner ad, in stream ad, ad placed in the content 128 itself, ad framing the content 128, an ad appearing before or after the content 128 and the like. A pause and resume 114 functionality may facilitate ad insertion at any point during the content without having to make the advertisement part of the content itself.
