In an embodiment, a pause and resume 114 functionality of a mobile media platform 100 may be associated with a variety of billing systems. For example, billing may be based on the amount of bandwidth consumed by the delivery of a piece or collection of content 128, which may be less than 100% if content was paused and never resumed.
